3月4日，鄧家希的喪禮在曼德勒舉行，大批民眾為她送殯，並做出反對專制的「[[三指禮|三指禮]]」，網上亦有許多人悼念她，稱她為「天使」及「英雄」<ref name="mp210305"/><ref>{{cite |title='She is a hero': In Myanmar's protests, women are on the front lines |date=2021-03-05 |work=The Straits Times |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MVaBsAKzaMY |accessdate=2021-03-06 |archive-date=2021-03-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210315183130/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MVaBsAKzaMY |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite |title=緬甸政變：民眾上街悼念被槍殺的華裔女子鄧家希 |date=2021-03-05 |work=自由亞洲電台 |url=https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/Xinwen/4-03052021095939.html |accessdate=2021-03-06 |archive-date=2021-05-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210518082315/https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/Xinwen/4-03052021095939.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。同时缅甸社交媒体上也开始流传军人在征得家属同意后挖开鄧家希坟墓的假新闻，引起缅甸人民对军方的众怒<ref>{{Cite web|author=黎秉辉|title=缅军挖邓家希坟墓？ · 实为挖炸弹旧视频|url=https://www.sinchew.com.my/content/content_2443247.html|date=2021-03-15|accessdate=2021-03-23|work=www.sinchew.com.my}}</ref>。翌日，軍人到她的墓地，以槍威脅墓地職員及封鎖入口，在未得家屬同意下強行挖墳起棺驗屍<ref>{{cite news |author=張寧倢 |title=恐怖挖墳影片曝光！緬甸19歲正妹遭爆頭　網瘋傳軍警「盜墓偷屍」 |work=ETtoday新聞雲 |date=2021-03-06 |url=https://www.ettoday.net/news/20210306/1932235.htm |accessdate=2021-03-07 |archive-date=2021-03-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210306134116/https://www.ettoday.net/news/20210306/1932235.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=緬甸19歲少女中槍亡　當局被指起棺驗屍再回葬 |date=2021-03-06 |newspaper=明報 |url=https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/article/20210306/s00005/1615035980871/%E7%B7%AC%E7%94%B819%E6%AD%B2%E5%B0%91%E5%A5%B3%E4%B8%AD%E6%A7%8D%E4%BA%A1-%E7%95%B6%E5%B1%80%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E8%B5%B7%E6%A3%BA%E9%A9%97%E5%B1%8D%E5%86%8D%E5%9B%9E%E8%91%AC |accessdate=2021-03-07 |archive-date=2021-03-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210306161046/https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/article/20210306/s00005/1615035980871/%E7%B7%AC%E7%94%B819%E6%AD%B2%E5%B0%91%E5%A5%B3%E4%B8%AD%E6%A7%8D%E4%BA%A1-%E7%95%B6%E5%B1%80%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E8%B5%B7%E6%A3%BA%E9%A9%97%E5%B1%8D%E5%86%8D%E5%9B%9E%E8%91%AC |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

